vote.title: A resolution authorizing the Mayor to appoint an Ad Hoc City Council Canvassing Committee to review the returns of the May 4, 2024 special election, and submit a canvass report to the full City Council on Wednesday, May 15, 2024 City Council meeting or at a special called city council meeting - Financing:  No cost consideration to the City
